name: ElJet
overview:
ElJet is a leading private jet charter company.

ElJet has the largest network of private jet charter and corporate jet charter fleets and schedules at our disposal. We have access to more than 4,000 private jet rental aircraft that fly to 15,000 airports domestically and internationally. It’s the most comprehensive inventory of private jet charter service information available, and it’s just one way in which ElJet separates itself from other private jet charter companies.

ElJet provides a one-stop shop for private jet charter and private plane charter rental services by offering our clients the option of purchasing an empty leg flight if one is available, or simply booking a traditional private plane charter. Many customers find that the empty leg option offers unexpected savings that they missed out on when booking private jet charter flights with other private jet charter companies. Whether you need a Light Private Jet for a smaller private plane charter flight or the glorious BBJ we will work exhaustively to locate the private jet of your choice at a price that is lower than our competition - guaranteed. Try finding that level of attention with other private jet charter services.
